data.description: Pool and Spa just in time for hot summer days!  Freeway close in the heart of Salida. This home features 1380 Sq.Ft. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths. Tile and wood flooring throughout the living areas. Updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Includes spacious master bedroom, featuring its own private access to the pool and the spa.
